longBusinessSummary: PT Bank China Construction Bank Indonesia Tbk provides various banking products and services in Indonesia. It operates through four segments: Loans, Treasury, Trade Finance, and Unallocated. The company offers various deposit products comprising savings and current accounts, and time deposits; auto and mortgage loans, and commercial express credit products; and safe deposits boxes, and treasury and international banking services. The company was formerly known as PT Bank Windu Kentjana International Tbk and changed its name to PT Bank China Construction Bank Indonesia Tbk in December 2016. The company was founded in 1974 and is headquartered in Jakarta Pusat, Indonesia. PT Bank China Construction Bank Indonesia Tbk operates as a subsidiary of China Construction Bank Corporation.
